{"type":"answer","id":181388,"parentType":"question","parentId":19511,"uid":3685,"contents":"听说有人要看伟大领袖的嘘法？那我就给你们贴一张<br>\n【不须放屁】1976年元旦，《人民日报》等各大报刊在头版刊发毛泽东的两首词，其一为《念奴娇·鸟儿问答》，作于1965年，后作修改，图为毛泽东手稿。“两报一刊”元旦社论称，发表这两首词“具有重大的政治意义和现实意义”。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DYxlo2eU8AAzQb-?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DYxlo2eU8AAzQb-?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DYxlo2eU8AAzQb-?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-02-27","agreeCount":10,"discussionCount":2}